Key → Heroicon mapping (svg/<key>.svg)
--------------------------------------

users      → user-group
atom       → cpu-chip          (semantic: scientific/technical)
ship       → arrows-pointing-out (semantic: voyage/deploy)
bomb       → no-symbol         (semantic: risk/blocker)
shield     → shield-check
fire       → fire
chart      → chart-bar
star       → star
lightning  → bolt
target     → flag              (semantic: target/objective)
brain      → sparkles          (semantic: intelligence/ideas)
gear       → cog-6-tooth
lock       → lock-closed
leaf       → sun               (semantic: growth/energy)
globe      → globe-alt
rocket     → rocket-launch
eye        → eye
check      → check
warning    → exclamation-triangle
idea       → light-bulb
clock      → clock
money      → currency-dollar
building   → building-office
network    → signal
book       → book-open
cloud      → cloud
code       → code-bracket
database   → circle-stack
mobile     → device-phone-mobile
palette    → swatch
